quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  46,1,Haa Miim
  46,2,"Bu’iinsi Qur’aanaa Rabbii injifataa, ogeeysa ta’e irraayi"
  46,3,"Samii, dachiifi waan isaan lamaan gidduu jiranis dhugaafi yeroo beekamaa ta’eef malee hin uumneIsaan kafaran waan ittiin sodaachifaman irraa garagaloodha"
  46,4,"(Yaa Muhammad!) jedhi: “wantoota Rabbiin ala gabbartan naaf himaa? Dachii irraa waan isaan uuman natti agarsiisaaMoo samii (uumuu) keessatti shariikummaan isaaniif jira? Yoo dhugaa dubbattoota taataniif mee kitaaba (Qur’aana) kana dura (bu’e) yookiin hambaa beekumsa durii wahii naaf dhiyeessaa.”"
  46,5,Nama Rabbiin ala waan hanga Guyyaa Qiyaamaatti homaa isaaf hin owwaanneefi isaan kadhaa isaanii irraa dagatoo ta’an gabbaru caalaa jallataan eenyu
  46,6,Yeroo ilmi namaa walitti qabamu diinota isaaniif ta’uIbaadaa isaaniittis kafaroo ta’u
  46,7,"Yeroo keeyyatoonni keenya ifa ta’anii isaan irratti dubbifaman, isaan kafaran dhugaan isaanitti dhufnaan “kun Sihrii ifa galaadha” jedhan"
  46,8,"Yookiin “(Muhammadtu SAW) sobaan isa uume” jedhu(Yaa Muhammad!) “yoo ani sobaan isa uumeef (adabbii) Rabbii irraa naaf tumsuu hin dandeessanuInni (Rabbiin) waan isin keessa galtan akkaan beekaadhaAnaafi isin giddutti ragaaf Inni ga’aadhaInni araaramaa, rahmata godhaadha” jedhi"
  46,9,"(Yaa Muhammad!) jedhi: “Ani ergamtoota irraa isa jalaqabaatii mitiWaan anaafi isin irratti dalagamuuf jirus hin beekuWaan gara kiyyatti wahyii godhamu malee (wanta biraa) hin hordofuAni sodaachisaa ifa bahaadha malee waan biraatii miti.”"
  46,10,"“Mee naaf himaa! Yoo (Qur’aanni kun) odoma isin itti kafartanuu Rabbi biraa ta’e, raga bahaan Ilmaan Israa’ilii irraa ta’e fakkaataa isaa irratti ragaa bahee yoo amanee isin immoo boontan, (isin miidhaa hin hojjannee)? Rabbiin miidhaa raawwattoota hin qajeelchu” jedhi"